00:50:10.260 --> 00:50:24.380
ben: optimizing zkVMs, but treat them more as a black box, and instead trying to make some changes in the Guest program so that they are more suitable. So I fixed on specific pair, which was ethrex and Zisk.

386
00:50:24.600 --> 00:50:32.060
ben: And then I'm planning to… hopefully make some generalizations, and how this can be extended to

387
00:50:32.210 --> 00:50:42.040
